subsystem: Imperative summary under ~50 chars (no trailing period)

# Body: wrap at 72 columns. Explain WHY this change is needed and what it
# does at a high level. The diff shows HOW. Reference issues/papers if useful.
#
# Component prefixes: raft store wal grpc proto cluster metrics k8s docker
#                     engine dashboard ci docs cmd
#
# Imperative mood: "Add", "Fix", "Remove" -- not "Added"/"Fixes".
# One logical change per commit.
#
# Sign off with `git commit -s` (adds the Signed-off-by line below / DCO):
# Signed-off-by: Radu Andrei Tudorica <raduandreitudorica3@gmail.com>
